question: are you still doing these? if so: sleeping with carol danvers? otherwise just ignore this lmao love your blog btw💕
answer:
I’m happy you like my blog pal

“Fuck…” 

You awake to the sound of her voice mixed with the shaking of the vanity. You stifle a yawn as you sit up in bed, spying Carol trying to quietly pick up the items that were now scattered on the floor.

“Carol?” You mumble quietly, rubbing your eyes slowly. “What are you doing?”

“I didn’t mean to wake you.” The blonde apologizes, a soft chuckle leaving her lips.  

“You coming to bed?”

“Mhmm,” she assures you, “I’ll be there in a minute.”

“Okay,” You lay back down, shuffling to get comfortable. “don’t take too long.”

“I won’t,” Carol disappears into the bathroom leaving you alone. You try to wait up for her but drowsiness takes over and you’re back to sleep before you know it.

summary:
Ngl I hated Captain Marvel for two reasons;
1) The Skrulls are evil bastards who love nothing more than to wage war on everyone....
body:
Ngl I hated Captain Marvel for two reasons;

1) The Skrulls are evil bastards who love nothing more than to wage war on everyone. They waged war on Xandar. They waged war on the Badoon they waged war on Karolina Dean’s race (I forget their name). They conquer, colonise and subjugate. They are just as bad as, if not worse than, the Kree. The suns never set on the Skrull Empire (or the Kree or even the Spartoi, but we’re not talking about them). They’re bloodthirsty, battle crazy and when they’re around you can’t even trust your pet goldfish.

But Marvel went and made them ‘victims’. Like no. Fuck that shit. I hate it. I want Secret Empire. I want a Fantastic Four movie. I want a second Fantastic Four movie where the Skrulls attack and Reed Richards hypnotises them into cows. Give me my evil Skrulls, you cowards!

2) The cat. Her name is Chewie. HER NAME IS CHEWIE.

body:
Thor: Can someone just…. explain French to me?

Carol: It’s Spanish but you speak it in cursive.

Bucky: Learn to speak Spanish. Now learn to speak Italian. Now subtract the Spanish from Italian. You are left with French.

Tony: Latin, but then make it fashion.

Natasha: Cover the second half of the word, squint, and pronounce only the vowels you think you see.

Peter: Gargling but with air.

summary: I dont know what else to say anymore. Im just... tired. Like...why? Why u have to do this? They were both great movies. Captain...
body:
Can this shit just stop

I dont know what else to say anymore. Im just… tired. Like…why? Why u have to do this? They were both great movies. Captain marvel was honestly better than endgame but y'all built that shit up so damn much it’s ridiculous. Sure it was a good ending to the original story arcs but as a movie it wasn’t actually as good as y'all think. The people who had problems with endgame cared for about a week but captain marvel been out for a while now and y'all still won’t shut up.

And let’s not forget the shit y'all gave wonder woman when it first came out. You don’t get to say It “worked where captain marvel failed” when you hated on it and Gal Gadot almost as much and you are now with Brie Larson. Just because a woman doesn’t fit your sexually driven ideas of what she should be you decide that means you have to treat her like shit and judge every little thing she does.

You can’t say it’s not sexism when Brie Larson gets nothing but hate just for not having a charismatic personality and got flooded with bad reviews before her movie came out but someone like Chris Pratt is willingly involved in an openly homophobic religion and gets next to no backlash.
